Prerequisites:
*python 2.4 or higher but with the 2.x
*python-qt4 
*macchanger
*xterm
*aircrack-ng


To launch the program use the icon at "/usr/share/applications" Or From Terminal:

$ python /usr/local/bin/Fern-Wifi-Cracker/execute.py

Please run in the above format if running from terminal, this is because the icons
used in the software are initialized, and the resolution is also adjusted to fit the applications
requirement when ran using the above argument..


